review.reviewBody: It was very delicious. I was disappointed to only get two small potatoes in my main dish. Im glad I ordered more on the side.
Taste was odd across the board. Do not recommend.

didnt have one major part of our order and didnt offer to substitute it  didnt offer anything didnt even contact us.  just immediately refunded the money and sent the other parts of the order we no longer needed.   so awkward Beef Souvlaki
The Gino's Burger was tasty with the fries. 3 star rating as they forgot to packmy  pop and I was charged for it
The beef souvlaki is so good it will make you cry.
